<script Name="prep_msDialog" When="BeforeShow">

	if (!this.IsPostBack) {
		
		gx.http.loadScript("MatiasSolucoes/msToastr/toastr.min.js", (function () {
						
			function toastrNotification(win) {
				function init(config) {
					win.toastr.options = config;
					
					return {
						toast
					};
				}
				
				function toast(type, title, content) {
					const notify = win.toastr[type];
					
					notify(content, title);
				}
				
				return {
					init
				};
			}
			
			(function () {
				if (!window.modules) window.modules = {};
				
				window.modules.notify = toastrNotification(window).init({
					"closeButton": this.closeButton,
					"debug": this.debug,
					"newestOnTop": this.newestOnTop,
					"progressBar": this.progressBar,
					"positionClass": this.positionClass,
					"preventDuplicates": this.preventDuplicates,
					"onclick": null,
					"showDuration": this.showDuration,
					"hideDuration": this.hideDuration,
					"timeOut": this.timeOut,
					"extendedTimeOut": this.extendedTimeOut,
					"showEasing": this.showEasing,
					"hideEasing": this.hideEasing,
					"showMethod": this.showMethod,
					"hideMethod": this.hideMethod
				});
			}.closure(this)());
			
			msToastr = (function() {
				const notify = window.modules.notify;
				
				return {
					MessagesGx: function (content) {
						const permittedTypes = ['warning', 'error', 'info', 'success'];
						
						for (const msg of content) {
							notify.toast(
							permittedTypes[msg.Type],
							'',
							msg.Description
							);
						}				
					},
					NotifyError: function (content) {
						notify.toast('error', '', content);
					},
					NotifyWarning: function (content) {
						notify.toast('warning', '', content);
					},
					NotifyInfo: function (content) {
						notify.toast('info', '', content);
					},
					NotifySuccess: function (content) {
						notify.toast('success', '', content);
					}
				};
			}());
			
		}).closure(this));
	}

</script>
